CustomField.description: Number of days notice the MSA says the customer must give if they intend to churn rather than auto-renew. This must be a whole number. Leave it blank if the MSA does not have auto-renew language.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: This must be a whole number. Leave it blank if the MSA does not have auto-renew language.
CustomField.label: Auto-Renew Term Notice Period In Days
